channel.title: Codingcommunity.org.. any one remember?- New Development Team!
channel.description:
Hi Everyone? Does any one remember codingcommunity.org? It was a website about coding in 2005. I bought the domain yesturday thinking we could be popular again.
If anyone would like to help me with the production & re-make of it, Please post here or PM me. You will recieve your very own email address. I am also offering free sub-domains for people who want them..
(you.codingcommunity.org)
You will get cpanel Access, mysql databases, emails and more!
So, please join the re-build of codingcommunity.org
Ikick
[b] www.codingcommunity.org [/b]
Site approved
